data.description: Make your appointment today to visit this beautiful home. Relax in the living room equipped with Gas fireplace. The flooring in the home is bamboo wood floors. Watch the golfers on the 11th hole  from your fully brick and window enclosed heated and cooled sunroom and also a view of the pond (you are permitted to fish in )  that is also adjacent to the 11th fairway and green. Home has 2 pet doors for larger dogs leading to the fenced backyard. (Currently no pets in the home)  Cooking in your spacious kitchen will be a delight with a large granite island. Eat in kitchen. Laundry has a utility sink. Washer and Dryer can remain if wanted.   Primary bedroom walks out onto the sunroom to enjoy your morning beverage.  Primary bathroom has a separate shower and tub.  Fourth bedroom upstairs with its own bathroom and pool table (if you would like it to stay) Two car garage has extra room for golf cart or riding lawn mower. One of the many outside spigots has HOT and cold water. Low maintenance flower beds with river rocks. (Not pine straw that needs replaced )  All of this on .46 acres of land.
